          Planta Almacenadora
        </span>

        <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-[3.25rem] font-bold text-alcasa-dark tracking-tight leading-[1.05]">
          Soluciones integrales para su <span class="text-alcasa-green">inventario agrícola</span>
        </h2>

        <p class="mt-6 text-lg text-alcasa-dark/70 font-light leading-relaxed max-w-2xl">
          Infraestructura diseñada para almacenar 100,000 toneladas en bodegas horizontales y 44,000 toneladas en silos de concreto.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="lg:col-span-4 lg:justify-self-end reveal opacity-0 translate-y-8 transition-all duration-1000 ease-out delay-[150ms]">
        <a
          href="/servicios"
          class="group inline-flex items-center gap-4 text-sm font-semibold text-alcasa-dark border border-alcasa-dark/20 px-6 py-4 rounded-xl bg-white/40 backdrop-blur-sm hover:border-alcasa-green hover:text-alcasa-green hover:bg-white transition-all duration-300 whitespace-nowrap"
        >
          <span>Ver todos los servicios</span>
          <span class="relative w-7 h-px bg-current transition-all duration-300 group-hover:w-9">
